{"tid":1081066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍研發腦機介面，飛行員可用大腦信號一次操控 3 架飛機","createTime":"2019-03-28T04:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T12:39:27.000Z","uid":225846,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"71af9c562e37985d2cfbde35614bb1108bf94be3","tid":1081066,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tomorrowsci.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/defense-large-678x325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftomorrowsci.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fdefense-large-678x325.jpg&h=b96d1132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內建腦波圖感測器的頭戴式裝置 / Credit : AP Photo/Nati Harnik<br />\n<br />\n美國國防高等研究計劃署（Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency, DARPA）一項腦機介面（brain-computer interfaces）新研究，允許飛行員透過大腦信號，同時控制多架模擬飛行器。<br />\n<br />\n腦機介面新突破<br />\n<br />\n事實上，2015 年 DARPA 就曾以一名四肢癱瘓的女性進行試驗，這名女性在腦部植入式微晶片後，就能駕駛一架 F-35 戰鬥機的模擬器。近日，DARPA 宣布此研究已經取得重大進展，允許飛行員同時操縱多架飛機。<br />\n<br />\n這是腦機介面領域的新進展。近年來科學發展迅速，在大腦溝通、義肢控制，甚至記憶修復方面都取得突破。自 2007 年以來，美國軍方一直在該領域研發相關研究。 2012 年， DARPA 投入 400 萬美元（約為 1 億 2 千萬台幣或 3,130 萬港幣），開發一種出非侵入式的腦機介面。該介面使用一個裝有腦波圖（electroencephalogram）感測器的頭戴式裝置，取得靠近大腦運動中心的大腦信號。<br />\n<br />\n真正的人機互動<br />\n除了同時控制多架飛機之外， DARPA 能夠改善飛行員和飛機之間的互動，使操作者不僅可以發送信號，還可以接收來自飛機的信號。讓飛行員能了解現況、發現威脅，並決定如何應對。<br />\n<br />\nDARPA 生物科技辦公室負責人賈斯汀&middot;桑切斯（Justin Sanchez）表示，時至今日，大腦信號可用於指揮和控制不僅一架飛機，他們已將技術擴展到三架飛機，並有完整的感官信號回傳。因此，飛行員一次可以操控多台飛機，大腦並可接收到飛機回傳的信號。<br />\n<br />\n桑切斯表示：「來自這些飛機的信號可以直接傳遞回大腦，讓飛行員的大腦也可以感知環境。這個問題耗費數年時間才獲得釐清。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n<br />\nTucker, P. (2018, September 06). It&rsquo;s Now Possible To Telepathically Communicate with a Drone Swarm. Retrieved September 30, 2018."},{"pid":"ea306a09a1f2f45a3bd6fb9fd4bf383a98a5ae19","tid":1081066,"uid":113922,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"零式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc62b7a6a3549875f63ae582e84661e3f468b6b","tid":1081066,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:01:52.000Z","msg":"同步率400%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b815db1d8e4f6d30140152742d640928a82263f5","tid":1081066,"uid":34641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"Professor X<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4b563041c958c3cefd3717f0e2c1657b509d61","tid":1081066,"uid":106233,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"激嬲佢"},{"pid":"a0eb71561182ea5667b51c90148450ed74da6ab0","tid":1081066,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79235d871f4b9a8cf675a25176247de4c5dcc2bd","tid":1081066,"uid":18012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:04:49.000Z","msg":"YF-21<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSkhkX-MmmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNSkhkX-MmmE&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AJa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=2e9034e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSkhkX-MmmE</a>"},{"pid":"ed1a7ecc88f92f4de83425b15fa7ee7cc3e68573","tid":1081066,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"EEG signal 咁多noise，留名睇炒機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6787b6d34b99649a1c8a69638528f67cfd7ff18","tid":1081066,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"牛油炮？"},{"pid":"b